<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        @page {
            margin: 0;
            size: A4 landscape;
        }
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            width: 297mm;
            height: 210mm;
        }
        .cert-wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            background-color: #fdfbff;
        }
        
        /* Corner Geometric Shapes */
        .shape-tl { position: absolute; top: -120px; left: -120px; width: 350px; height: 350px; background: #3b0764; transform: rotate(45deg); z-index: 1; }
        .shape-tl-inner { position: absolute; top: -60px; left: -60px; width: 200px; height: 200px; background: #6d28d9; transform: rotate(45deg); z-index: 2; }
        
        .shape-br { position: absolute; bottom: -150px; right: -150px; width: 450px; height: 450px; background: #4c1d95; transform: rotate(45deg); z-index: 1; }
        .shape-br-inner { position: absolute; bottom: -80px; right: -80px; width: 250px; height: 250px; background: #7c3aed; transform: rotate(45deg); z-index: 2; }

        .shape-tr { position: absolute; top: -100px; right: -50px; width: 200px; height: 200px; background: #a78bfa; transform: rotate(15deg); opacity: 0.4; z-index: 1; }
        .shape-bl { position: absolute; bottom: -100px; left: -50px; width: 250px; height: 250px; background: #ede9fe; transform: rotate(-15deg); z-index: 1; }

        /* Floating Accents */
        .accent-1 { position: absolute; top: 15%; right: 20%; width: 40px; height: 40px; background: #6d28d9; transform: rotate(45deg); z-index: 1; opacity: 0.7; }
        .accent-2 { position: absolute; bottom: 20%; left: 15%; width: 30px; height: 30px; background: #3b0764; transform: rotate(10deg); z-index: 1; }

        /* Content Area */
        .content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 60px;
            width: 80%;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .header-box {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .main-title {
            font-size: 64px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin: 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 6px;
        }
        .text-sep {
            width: 100px;
            height: 4px;
            background: #6d28d9;
            margin: 15px auto;
        }
        .sub-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #4b5563;
            font-weight: normal;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .intro-text {
            margin-top: 40px;
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #6d28d9;
            font-style: italic;
            font-family: 'Times-Roman', serif;
        }

        .name-container {
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .student-name {
            font-size: 60px;
            font-family: 'Times-BoldItalic', serif;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0 60px 5px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #3b0764;
        }

        .achievement-details {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #374151;
            line-height: 1.5;
            max-width: 80%;
            margin: 20px auto;
            font-family: 'Times-Roman', serif;
        }
        .course-name {
            color: #3b0764;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: block;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .message {
            margin-top: 35px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6b7280;
            max-width: 75%;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer-table {
            margin-top: 60px;
            display: table;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .footer-cell {
            display: table-cell;
            width: 50%;
            vertical-align: bottom;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .signature-text {
            font-family: 'Times-BoldItalic', serif;
            font-size: 28px;
            color: #3b0764;
            margin-bottom: -5px;
        }
        .line {
            width: 240px;
            border-top: 2px solid #1a1a1a;
            margin: 5px auto;
        }
        .label {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4b5563;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .date {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1a1a1a;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="cert-wrapper">
        <div class="shape-tl"></div>
        <div class="shape-tl-inner"></div>
        <div class="shape-br"></div>
        <div class="shape-br-inner"></div>
        <div class="shape-tr"></div>
        <div class="shape-bl"></div>
        
        <div class="accent-1"></div>
        <div class="accent-2"></div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="header-box">
                <h1 class="main-title">CERTIFICAT</h1>
                <div class="text-sep"></div>
                <div class="sub-title">DE RÉUSSITE</div>
            </div>

            <div class="intro-text">Ce certificat est fièrement décerné à :</div>
            
            <div class="name-container">
                <div class="student-name">{{ quizResult.studentName }}</div>
            </div>

            <div class="achievement-details">
                Pour avoir complété avec succès le quiz de la leçon :
                <span class="course-name">« {{ quizResult.lessonTitle }} »</span>
                dans le cadre de la formation <strong>{{ quizResult.formationTitle }}</strong>
            </div>

            <p class="message">
                « Félicitations pour cette réussite exceptionnelle ! Votre détermination et votre soif d'apprendre sont les clés de votre succès futur. Continuez à explorer et à grandir avec Finora. »
            </p>

            <div class="footer-table">
                <div class="footer-cell">
                    <div class="date">{{ quizResult.takenAt|date('d/m/Y') }}</div>
                    <div class="line"></div>
                    <div class="label">DATE D'OBTENTION</div>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-cell">
                    <div class="signature-text">Direction Finora</div>
                    <div class="line"></div>
                    <div class="label">SIGNATURE AUTORISÉE</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
